{"tid":1201321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳浩天呼籲抗爭者用絕對安全真正匿名嘅8chan傾計劃","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:07:05.000Z","uid":70063,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f907078233ead8f745f81b7cd13759e6e663cb","tid":1201321,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"[係時候升級喇!] 請用絕對安全真正匿名嘅8ch傾project!<br />\n<a href=\"https://8ch.net/hkpol/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F8ch.net%2Fhkpol%2F&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=bd716996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://8ch.net/hkpol/</a><br />\n<br />\n*****直接去重點*****<br />\n 唔需要註冊全匿名即刻留言，從來未試過交過IP俾任何政府<br />\n*******************<br />\n好多新人加入抗爭行列，但經驗不足，容易有危險。眼見好多人係一個兩萬人公海group講計劃，但心存僥倖覺得冇差佬冇記者，又有好多係FB同連登度講行動，睇見都好牙煙。所以建議大家可以好似鬼佬咁用8ch，唔需要註冊全匿名即刻留言，從來未試過交過IP俾任何政府。<br />\n<br />\n介紹番:<br />\n- 8ch個server喺美國<br />\n- 持有人係日本2channel同埋美國人Jim Watkins<br />\n- 全匿名制<br />\n- 可以自己del post，IP record會跟住個post一齊死<br />\n- 開post同留言都可以share好多檔案格式：jpg, gif, mp4, swf, pdf<br />\n- 8ch係頁底有warrant canary，從來未交過任何IP俾政府!<br />\n- 受FB Google封殺，所以係FB share 8ch啲link可能當spam，要係URL入面加個space<br />\n<br />\n8ch嘅少少背景:<br />\n8ch係由於4chan嘅/pol/版同/v/版版主政治審查del post，所以啲人再新開出嚟。本來4chan都視為痴線佬聚集嘅地方，例如極右痴線佬，同埋又會有好多落地獄嘅memes。而8ch就係痴線中嘅痴線，最近嘅例子就係紐西蘭槍擊案槍手行動前，係8ch發表宣言。當然我唔係叫大家做同樣嘅事情，但香港呢個地方本來就好痴線，我地係香港呢個地方抗爭更痴線，用8ch都不為過。希望各位痴線佬安安全全，致新加入嘅痴線佬:「Don't die on the first day.」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2400355456850847&amp;id=1791959604357105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2400355456850847%26id%3D1791959604357105&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=9660a993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2400355456850847&amp;id=1791959604357105</a>"},{"pid":"053b2ada1fb68ea9dd02b8edcd605a818b313d5e","tid":1201321,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e4d3c595b2b5bd6c797a7d3d8e354be9f57db9c9","tid":1201321,"uid":21038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"佢唔潛水行出黎即上神枱 家陣群雄無首 要有個知名人士敢企出黎帶嘅 入冊入得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea9691beaae33630b9c4bbd0476dbcdc86d9115","tid":1201321,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d3c595b2b5bd6c797a7d3d8e354be9f57db9c9","tid":1201321,"uid":21038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"佢唔潛水行出黎即上神枱 家陣群雄無首 要有個知名人士敢企出黎帶嘅 入冊入得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢嗰條社團條例搞成點"},{"pid":"b747cc83331301e55df61cc0f189856cd71e0bbd","tid":1201321,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cea9691beaae33630b9c4bbd0476dbcdc86d9115","tid":1201321,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d3c595b2b5bd6c797a7d3d8e354be9f57db9c9","tid":1201321,"uid":21038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"佢唔潛水行出黎即上神枱 家陣群雄無首 要有個知名人士敢企出黎帶嘅 入冊入得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢嗰條社團條例搞成點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"放棄左上訴<br />\n但佢可以用個人身份或者另外整一個團體"},{"pid":"c5a9c17362149ff912c06b9273039fce0f776284","tid":1201321,"uid":131691,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"On topic: 整咗個8ch香港台今日終於有用有人賞識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b98028a939a69af290fbec0144a5fa9bb9a2510","tid":1201321,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5a9c17362149ff912c06b9273039fce0f776284","tid":1201321,"uid":131691,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T09